title: Video: In Donbass, Russell “Texas” Bentley investigates MH17
text:
The final report about MH17 flight crash has been released today [October 13] in the Netherlands . Despite a year having passed since the catastrophe the official investigation didn’t shed any light upon the case. Therefore “Texas” (Russell Bonner Bentley) decided to make his own investigation.
Boeing MH17 - Russell Bentley ('Texas') investigation in Donbass
